DependencyRules:
//Acrescentado a dependency0.xip pelo professor Nuno Mamede (21/06/2010)
//|NP{art[masc], noun[masc=+]}| ~
//|NP{art[fem], noun[fem=+]}| ~
//|NP{art[sg], noun[sg=+]}| ~
//|NP{art[pl], noun[pl=+]}| ~

//|PP{art[masc], noun[masc=+]}| ~
